            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Shuttle services</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-headset" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M8 1a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v1h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H3a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V6a6 6 0 1 1 12 0v6a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-2.5 2.5H9.366a1 1 0 0 1-.866.5h-1a1 1 0 1 1 0-2h1a1 1 0 0 1 .866.5H11.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 13 12h-1a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V8a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h1V6a5 5 0 0 0-5-5z" />
                    </svg>24/7 customer service.
                </p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-car-front-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
